commit a44ac58af394245c1363629ba9d2de6ee6936d34
Author: Christoph Brill <egore@gmx.de>
Date:	2012-05-22

    Do not install any parts of colord-sane if --disable-sane is specified

    Signed-off-by: Richard Hughes <richard@hughsie.com>

